%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nawab%20Malik's%20Right%20To%20Health%20Not%20Curtailed%2C%20Says%20High%20Court%2C%20Refuses%20Bail%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENationalist%20Congress%20Party%20leader%20Nawab%20Malik%20is%20getting%20%26quot%3Bspecialized%20medical%20assistance%26quot%3B%20and%20his%20right%20to%20health%20or%20right%20to%20life%20is%20not%20infringed%20in%20any%20manner%2C%20said%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20while%20refusing%20him%20medical%20bail%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20being%20probed%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20HC%20further%20said%20Malik's%20medical%20report%20does%20not%20indicate%20he%20is%20suffering%20from%20any%20critical%20ailment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20the%20report%20says%20the%20former%20state%20minister%20does%20not%20need%20further%20hospitalization%2C%20the%20HC%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20single%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Anuja%20Prabhudessai%20had%20rejected%20Malik's%20plea%20seeking%20bail%20on%20medical%20grounds%20on%20July%2013.%20The%20detailed%20order%20was%20made%20available%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalik%20was%20arrested%20in%20February%202022%20by%20the%20ED%20in%20a%20case%20linked%20to%20alleged%20activities%20of%20fugitive%20gangster%20Dawood%20Ibrahim%20and%20his%20associates.%20He%20is%20in%20judicial%20custody%20and%20currently%20undergoing%20treatment%20in%20a%20private%20hospital%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalik's%20counsel%20Amit%20Desai%20had%20argued%20his%20client's%20health%20was%20deteriorating%20over%20the%20last%20eight%20months%20and%20he%20was%20in%20stage%202%20to%20stage%203%20of%20chronic%20kidney%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%2C%20the%20HC%20bench%20said%20there%20can%20be%20no%20dispute%20that%20the%20right%20to%20health%20is%20recognized%20as%20an%20important%20facet%20of%20Article%2021%20(of%20the%20Constitution).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20right%20available%20to%20every%20person%2C%20including%20an%20under%20trial%20prisoner%20or%20convict.%20In%20fact%2C%20failure%20of%20the%20state%20to%20provide%20proper%20medical%20aid%20to%20prisoners%2C%20who%20are%20largely%20dependent%20on%20the%20jail%20authorities%2C%20would%20be%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20right%20guaranteed%20under%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20HC%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20instant%20case%2C%20Malik%20has%20several%20pre-existing%20ailments%2C%20it%20observed.%20He%20was%20admitted%20to%20the%20state-run%20JJ%20Hospital%20in%20Mumbai%20from%20February%2025%20to%2028%2C%202022%20and%20on%20subsequent%20dates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20admitted%20and%20is%20being%20treated%20in%20Criti%20Care%20Asia%2C%20a%20multi%20specialty%20hospital%20of%20his%20choice%2C%20since%20May%2017%2C%202022.%20The%20applicant%20is%20provided%20adequate%2C%20effective%20and%20specialized%20medical%20assistance%2C%20and%20his%20health%20condition%20is%20being%20monitored%20by%20the%20doctors%20specialized%20in%20the%20field.%20Hence%2C%20his%20right%20to%20health%20or%20right%20to%20life%20is%20not%20curtailed%20or%20infringed%20in%20any%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20was%20of%20the%20view%20that%20there%20can%20be%20no%20straight%20jacket%20formula%20in%20cases%20of%20medical%20bail%20and%20exercise%20of%20discretion%20under%20the%20proviso%20depends%20on%20facts%20and%20circumstances%20of%20each%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20thumb%20rule%20essentially%20is%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20sickness%2C%20health%20condition%20as%20well%20as%20availability%20of%20specialized%20and%20sustained%20medical%20treatment%20to%20the%20inmates%20confined%20within%20the%20four%20walls%20of%20the%20jail%2C%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20medical%20report%20of%20Malik%20does%20not%20indicate%20the%20applicant%20is%20suffering%20from%20any%20critical%20ailment%20or%20that%20his%20right%20kidney%20is%20functioning%20in%20a%20compromised%20manner.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20the%20report%20states%20that%20the%20applicant%20does%20not%20need%20further%20hospitalization%2C%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20medical%20board%20to%20examine%20the%20health%20condition%20of%20the%20accused%20was%20constituted%20on%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20HC%20and%20its%20report%20reveals%20he%20has%20a%20small%20left%20kidney%20with%20few%20benign%20cysts%20and%20a%20solitary%20functioning%20right%20kidney%2C%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20does%20not%20indicate%20the%20right%20kidney%20of%20the%20applicant%20has%20deteriorated%20or%20that%20it%20is%20functioning%20only%20at%2060%20per%20cent%20(as%20claimed%20by%20the%20accused).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20otherwise%20does%20not%20indicate%20that%20the%20applicant%20is%20suffering%20from%20any%20such%20chronic%20illness%2C%20which%20justifies%20grant%20of%20medical%20bail%2C%20the%20court%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20is%20expected%20to%20hear%20his%20plea%20seeking%20bail%20on%20merits%20after%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED's%20case%20against%20Malik%20is%20based%20on%20an%20FIR%20filed%20by%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20against%20Dawood%20Ibrahim%2C%20a%20designated%20global%20terrorist%20and%20a%20key%20accused%20in%20the%201993%20Mumbai%20serial%20bomb%20blasts%2C%20and%20his%20associates%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689440700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-06%2F2mmnn2kc_nawab-malik-ncp-leader-pti_625x300_10_June_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnawab-maliks-right-to-health-not-curtailed-says-high