Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fbiz%2Fnews%2Fsag-actor-strike-contract-sticking-points-1235670826%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fbiz%2Fnews%2Fsag-actor-strike-contract-sticking-points-1235670826%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Project%20Cheetah%3A%20Radio%20Collar%20Infections%20a%20'Cause%20for%20Concern'%2C%20Team%20Expert%20Questions%20Ground%20Support%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F01124706%2FFr_KjcBXoAEm2rW.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EKochi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%E2%80%99s%20been%20a%20bad%20week%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20Project%20Cheetah.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20cheetah%20Tejas%20died%20in%20its%20enclosure.%20The%20cause%2C%20authorities%20said%2C%20was%20a%20wound%20just%20above%20the%20neck%2C%20possibly%20inflicted%20by%20a%20female.%20A%20post-mortem%20showed%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cinternally%20weak%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20animal%20had%20succumbed%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctraumatic%20shock%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20another%20cheetah%2C%20also%20from%20South%20Africa%20%E2%80%93%20named%20Surya%20%E2%80%93%20died.%20Authorities%20noticed%20wounds%20on%20its%20neck%2C%20and%20back.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20experts%20have%20said%20that%20the%20cheetahs%E2%80%99%20deaths%20were%20due%20to%20infected%20wounds%20caused%20by%20the%20radio%20collars%20around%20their%20necks.%20It%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccause%20for%20concern%E2%80%9D%2C%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Cheetah%20Project%20Steering%20Committee%2C%20Rajesh%20Gopal%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20cheetahs%20fitted%20with%20radio%20collars%20will%20now%20be%20inspected%2C%20and%20a%20detailed%20health%20check%20up%20done%2C%20he%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20%E2%80%9Cunfortunate%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20deaths%20are%20not%20a%20setback%20to%20Project%20Cheetah%2C%20he%20added.%20However%2C%20where%20is%20the%20accountability%2C%20ask%20experts%2C%20and%20how%20can%20we%20expect%20cheetahs%20to%20help%20save%20grasslands%20when%20they%20cannot%20even%20save%20themselves.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20South%20Africa-based%20wildlife%20veterinarian%20who%20is%20also%20part%20of%20the%20Steering%20Committee%20has%20raised%20serious%20concerns%20regarding%20cheetah%20management%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20Kuno.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECollar-related%20infections%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20patrolling%20team%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Kuno%20National%20Park%20%E2%80%93%20where%20India%E2%80%99s%20Project%20Cheetah%20is%20unfolding%20%E2%80%93%20found%20the%20cheetah%20named%20Suraj%20dead%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20July%2014.%20It%20had%20a%20wound%20on%20its%20back.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuraj%2C%20which%20was%20brought%20from%20South%20Africa%20and%20had%20been%20released%20into%20the%20wild%20in%20Kuno%2C%20is%20the%20eighth%20cheetah%20to%20die%20in%20India%20as%20part%20of%20Project%20Cheetah.%20The%20programme%20aims%20to%20introduce%20the%20African%20cheetah%20into%20select%20central%20Indian%20grasslands%2C%20where%20the%20Asiatic%20subspecies%20used%20to%20roam%20till%20around%2075%20years%20ago.%20The%20idea%20is%20that%20these%20charismatic%20animals%20will%20help%20save%20India%E2%80%99s%20grasslands%2C%20which%20face%20numerous%20threats.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwenty%20adult%20cheetahs%20arrived%20in%20Kuno%20from%20Namibia%20and%20South%20Africa%20since%20September%20last%20year.%20Of%20these%2C%20five%20are%20now%20dead%20(cheetah%20Sasha%20was%20the%20first%20to%20die%2C%20of%20renal%20failure%20on%20March%2027%20this%20year).%20Three%20cubs%20born%20to%20Namibian%20cheetah%20Jwala%20have%20also%20died.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20on%20July%2011%2C%20the%20monitoring%20team%20found%20that%20four-year-old%20male%20Tejas%20had%20a%20wound%20on%20his%20neck.%20Before%20they%20could%20capture%20and%20treat%20him%2C%20he%20died%20in%20his%20enclosure.%20The%20wound%20was%20probably%20inflicted%20by%20a%20female%20during%20the%20animals%E2%80%99%20interactions%2C%20forest%20officials%20had%20said.%20The%20post-mortem%20showed%20that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Cinternally%20weak%E2%80%9D%20and%20was%20unable%20to%20recover%20from%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctraumatic%20shock%E2%80%9D%20after%20a%20violent%20fight%20with%20the%20female%20cheetah%2C%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2Fnorth-and-central%2Fcheetah-tejas-died-as-he-could-not-recover-from-traumatic-shock-post-violent-fight-reveals-post-mortem-report-1236500.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enews%20reports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20both%20Tejas%20and%20Suraj%20died%20due%20to%20the%20same%20cause%3A%20collar-related%20infections%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fwildlife-veterinarians-blames-neck-collars-for-two-cheetah-deaths-in-kuno-national-park%2Fcid%2F1952108%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaccording%20to%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Adrian%20Tordiffe%2C%20a%20South%20Africa-based%20veterinarian%20who%20is%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20Cheetah%20Project%20Steering%20Committee.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETordiffe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fwildlife-veterinarians-blames-neck-collars-for-two-cheetah-deaths-in-kuno-national-park%2Fcid%2F1952108%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20Suraj%20died%20due%20to%20septicaemia%20(an%20infection%20of%20the%20bloodstream)%20caused%20on%20its%20neck%20by%20the%20radio%20collar%2C%20a%20device%20used%20to%20track%20animal%20movement.%20The%20humid%20or%20wet%20weather%20could%20have%20caused%20water%20to%20accumulate%20underneath%20the%20collar%2C%20keeping%20the%20skin%20constantly%20wet%2C%20Tordiffe%20had%20said.%20Flies%20attracted%20to%20the%20spot%20lay%20eggs%20and%20the%20maggots%20that%20emerge%20%E2%80%9Cfeed%20on%20tissues%20and%20create%20wounds%20that%20get%20infected%20and%20can%20lead%20to%20systemic%20infection%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20%5Bcheetahs%20Tejas%20and%20Suraj%20died%20due%20to%20collar-related%20infections%5D%20is%20true%20and%20it%20is%20a%20cause%20for%20concern%20because%20in%20my%20career%20I%E2%80%99ve%20never%20seen%20radio%20collars%20giving%20problems%20like%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rajesh%20Gopal%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20Cheetah%20Project%20Steering%20Committee.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGopal%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20Project%20Tiger%20for%20more%20than%2030%20years%20and%20has%2C%20among%20others%2C%20overseen%20radio-collaring%20in%20wild%20tigers.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20clear%20cut%20case%20of%20abrasion%20and%20degenerating%20into%20sepsis%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F09223936%2FModi-cheetah-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F09223936%2FModi-cheetah-1.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F09223936%2FModi-cheetah-1-300x167.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F09223936%2FModi-cheetah-1-1024x569.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-652374%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20looks%20at%20one%20of%20the%20cheetah%20at%20the%20Kuno%20National%20Park.%20Photo%3A%20PMO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDeaths%20%E2%80%9Cunfortunate%E2%80%9D%20but%20not%20a%20setback%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETordiffe%2C%20associate%20professor%20and%20veterinary%20wildlife%20specialist%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pretoria%2C%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20he%20immediately%20knew%20that%20the%20infections%20were%20caused%20by%20the%20radio%20collars%20when%20he%20saw%20the%20video%20clip%20of%20Surya%20that%20field%20personnel%20took%20before%20the%20post-mortem.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20the%20cheetahs%20in%20Kuno%20are%20currently%20fitted%20with%20African%20Wildlife%20Tracking%20(AWT)%20collars%2C%20Tordiffe%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20widely%20used%20in%20South%20Africa%20and%20are%20normally%20very%20good.%20This%20issue%20%5Bof%20infections%5D%20has%20never%20cropped%20up%20with%20AWT%20collars%20before.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20strange%E2%80%9D%20that%20these%20radiocollars%20are%20causing%20infections%20because%20these%20are%20state-of-the-art%20synthetic%20collars%2C%20and%20a%20standard%20procedure%20is%20followed%20to%20fit%20them%2C%20Gopal%20said.%20All%20cheetahs%20fitted%20with%20radio%20collars%20will%20now%20be%20inspected%2C%20and%20a%20detailed%20health%20check%20up%20%E2%80%93%20in%20addition%20to%20other%20existing%20health%20checks%20%E2%80%93%20will%20be%20done%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20though%20%E2%80%9Cunfortunate%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20deaths%20are%20not%20a%20setback%20to%20Project%20Cheetah%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20won%E2%80%99t%20affect%20the%20project%20because%20the%20project%20area%20is%20characterised%20by%20a%20large%20number%20of%20births%20and%20deaths%2C%20that%20is%20how%20we%20envision%20the%20cheetah%20landscape%2C%20only%20then%20it%20becomes%20productive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChallenges%20such%20as%20the%20cheetah%20deaths%20will%20occur%20but%20these%20are%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20insurmountable%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20cheetah%20habitats%20would%20not%20be%20fenced%20off%2C%20as%20fencing%20%E2%80%9Cgoes%20against%20the%20tenets%20of%20conservation%20in%20India%E2%80%9D.%20The%20fencing%20occurring%20at%20the%20Gandhi%20Sagar%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20is%20for%20the%20in-situ%20conservation%20of%20the%20next%20batch%20of%20cheetahs%20that%20will%20come%20to%20India%2C%20and%20small%20enclosures%20of%20four%20to%20ten%20hectares%20in%20size%20are%20being%20made%20to%20augment%20prey%20in%20the%20landscape%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20when%20will%20the%20next%20batch%20arrive%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20decision%20is%20not%20yet%20made%20and%20the%20existing%20cheetahs%20need%20to%20%E2%80%9Cstabilise%20first%E2%80%9D%2C%20Gopal%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6These%20animals%20brought%20from%20another%20destination%20%5Bhave%20to%20face%5D%20obvious%20changes%20in%20temperature%2C%20humidity%2C%20day%20and%20night%20durations%2C%20encountering%20a%20new%20set%20of%20prey%2C%20their%20anti-predator%20strategies%20and%20alarms%20are%20different%E2%80%A6%5Bthey%5D%20need%20to%20fine%20tune%20their%20behavioural%20patterns%20in%20the%20context%20of%20feeding%2C%20adjusting%2C%20separating%20to%20avoid%20clashes%20(food%20and%20shelter%20niches%20with%20another%20co-predator%20operating%20there%2C%20which%20is%20the%20leopard)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F20162049%2FFpPKPzyaUAIUrGc.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F20162049%2FFpPKPzyaUAIUrGc.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F20162049%2FFpPKPzyaUAIUrGc-300x154.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F20162049%2FFpPKPzyaUAIUrGc-1024x524.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-641251%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22614%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20cheetah%20from%20South%20Africa%20that%20was%20translocated%20to%20Kuno%20National%20Park.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40byadavbjp%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhere%20is%20accountability%2C%20experts%20ask%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-item-key%3D%5C%221689439463.006589%5C%22%20tabindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20data-qa%3D%5C%22virtual-list-item%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-qa-placeholder%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20data-qa-unprocessed%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20data-qa%3D%5C%22message_container%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-qa-hover%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-qa%3D%5C%22message_content%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-qa%3D%5C%22message-text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-qa%3D%5C%22block-kit-renderer%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3EBut%20how%20are%20authorities%20expecting%20the%20animals%20to%20%E2%80%9Cfine%20tune%E2%80%9D%20when%20each%20time%20they%20go%20anywhere%20officials%20do%20not%20want%20them%20to%20they%20are%20brought%20back%20to%20Kuno%20or%20when%20they%20get%20involved%20in%20intra-specific%20conflicts%2C%20they%20are%20returned%20to%20captivity%2C%20asks%20big%20cat%20expert%20Ravi%20Chellam.%20Chellam%20has%20spent%20decades%20studying%20and%20engaging%20with%20the%20conservation%20of%20Asiatic%20lions%20in%20Gir.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChellam%2C%20who%20has%20been%20critical%20of%20Project%20Cheetah%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fkuno-project-cheetah-carrying-capacity%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eseveral%20reasons%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20incidents%20where%20two%20cheetahs%20Pavan%20and%20Aasha%20were%20captured%20and%20brought%20back%20to%20Kuno%20when%20the%20animals%20ranged%20outside%20the%20Park%20and%20into%20adjoining%20villages%20and%20fields%3B%20and%20when%20two%20male%20cheetahs%20Vayu%20and%20Agni%20were%20captured%20to%20treat%20their%20injuries%20sustained%20in%20an%20interaction%20with%20another%20cheetah%20male%20coalition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoreover%2C%20if%20the%20deaths%20are%20a%20result%20of%20injuries%20caused%20by%20radio%20collars%2C%20then%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cclearly%20human%20error%E2%80%9D%2C%20Chellam%2C%20who%20also%20used%20radio-telemetry%20to%20study%20lions%20in%20Gir.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20this%20had%20happened%20to%20animals%20radio-collared%20by%20a%20wildlife%20researcher%2C%20their%20research%20permits%20would%20have%20been%20cancelled%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWhere%20is%20the%20accountability%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConducting%20a%20health%20examination%20of%20the%20remaining%20cheetahs%20and%20testing%20their%20radio%20collars%20would%20mean%20darting%20and%20capturing%20the%20animals%2C%20thus%20putting%20them%20under%20stress%20again%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20expressed%20dismay%20at%20the%20number%20of%20cheetah%20deaths%20so%20far.%20All%20deaths%20except%20the%20last%20(that%20of%20Surya%20on%20July%2014)%20have%20occurred%20within%20the%20cheetah%20enclosures%2C%20where%20the%20cats%20are%20under%20constant%20monitoring%20and%20management%20by%20the%20field%20team%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20mating-related%20deaths%20(a%20female%20named%20Daksha%20died%20during%20a%20violent%20mating%20interaction%20with%20two%20males%20within%20an%20enclosure%20on%20May%209)%20could%20have%20been%20easily%20avoided.%20The%20project%20smacks%20of%20poor%20planning%20and%20weak%20management%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20effort%20is%20farcical%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20project%20is%20based%20on%20poor%20science%20and%20completely%20unviable%20conservation%20goals.%20What%20are%20we%20trying%20to%20do%3F%20We%20want%20to%20use%20the%20cheetahs%20to%20try%20and%20save%20our%20grasslands%20and%20its%20denizens%20including%20the%20Great%20Indian%20bustard%2C%20but%20the%20cheetahs%20cannot%20even%20save%20themselves.%20Who%20will%20be%20held%20responsible%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EConcerns%20regarding%20cheetah%20management%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETordiffe%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20said%20he%20has%20raised%20some%20serious%20concerns%20about%20the%20level%20of%20veterinary%20care%20available%20at%20Kuno.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20major%20concern%20is%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20senior%20scientist%20at%20Kuno%20to%20coordinate%20the%20management%20and%20monitoring%20of%20the%20animals%2C%20Tordiffe%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Initially%2C%20the%20project%20was%20overseen%20on%20the%20ground%20by%20Y.V.Jhala%2C%20then%20dean%20of%20the%20Wildlife%20Institute%20of%20India%2C%20and%20his%20students%2C%20Tordiffe%20said.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20he%20was%20forced%20to%20retire%2C%20much%20of%20that%20flew%20out%20the%20window%20and%20currently%2C%20it%20is%20just%20managed%20by%20forest%20department%20personnel.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20something%20we%20seriously%20need%20to%20address%E2%80%A6for%20such%20a%20high%20profile%20project%2C%20I%20absolutely%20do%20think%20we%20need%20a%20senior%20scientist%20at%20Kuno%20coordinating%20the%20management%20and%20monitoring%20of%20the%20animals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20raised%20this%20issue%20with%20the%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority%20(which%20is%20implementing%20Project%20Cheetah)%2C%20Tordiffe%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20what%20of%20the%20remaining%20cheetahs%3F%20Should%20their%20collars%20come%20off%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20this%20stage%2C%20the%20need%20is%20to%20assess%20how%20extensive%20the%20issue%20is%20%E2%80%93%20how%20many%20cheetahs%20are%20affected%20by%20the%20radio%20collars%2C%20and%20to%20what%20extent%2C%20Tordiffe%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20If%20their%20wounds%20are%20minor%2C%20they%20can%20be%20treated%20with%20long-acting%20antibiotics%20and%20insecticides%20on%20their%20skins%20which%20will%20prevent%20maggots%20from%20damaging%20their%20skin%2C%20he%20said.%20But%20such%20treatment%20would%20mean%20bringing%20the%20free-ranging%20animals%20back%20to%20camp%2C%20removing%20their%20collars%20and%20ensuring%20they%20are%20in%20enclosures%20until%20the%20monsoon%20is%20over%20(since%20wet%20conditions%20would%20mean%20that%20repeated%20treatments%20are%20required).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMike%20Toft%2C%20a%20wildlife%20veterinarian%20who%20has%20vast%20experience%20treating%20cheetahs%20in%20Phinda%20reserve%20will%20most%20likely%20reach%20Kuno%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20assist%20with%20the%20assessment%20of%20the%20other%20cheetahs%2C%20Tordiffe%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689440377000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F01124706%2FFr_KjcBXoAEm2rW.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fproject-cheetah-deaths-radio-collar-infections%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Where%20is%20the%20accountability%2C'%20ask%20independent%20experts%2C%20after%20the%20death%20of%20eight%20cheetahs%20at%20Kuno.%20The%20South%20African%20vet%20on%20the%20steering%20committee%20has%20also%20raised%20concerns%20regarding%20cheetah%20management%20on%20the%20ground.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fproject-cheetah-deaths-radio-collar-infections%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Simon%20Cowell%20says%20the%20sexual%20assault%20of%20a%20former%20'X%20Factor'%20contestant%20was%20'horrific%20and%20heart-breaking'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221928%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22simon%20cowell%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b2b9a79751e300192a3c41%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221446%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESimon%20Cowell%20created%20The%20X%20Factor%20and%20has%20been%20a%20judge%20on%20both%20the%20US%20and%20UK%20versions.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESimon%20Cowell%20said%20the%20sexual%20assault%20of%20an%20%26quot%3BX%20Factor%26quot%3B%20contestant%20was%20%26quot%3Bhorrific%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bheartbreaking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELucy%20Spraggan%20told%20The%20Guardian%20she%20was%20raped%20by%20a%20hotel%20porter%20while%20competing%20on%20the%20show.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20was%20critical%20of%20the%20support%20offered%20by%20the%20show's%20producers%20after%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESimon%20Cowell%20described%20the%20sexual%20assault%20of%20a%20former%20%26quot%3BX%20Factor%26quot%3B%20contestant%20as%20%26quot%3Bhorrific%20and%20heart-breaking%26quot%3B%20after%20she%20criticized%20the%20support%20provided%20by%20the%20show's%20producers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELucy%20Spraggan%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftv-and-radio%2F2023%2Fjul%2F15%2Flucy-spraggan-the-real-reason-i-dropped-out-of-the-x-factor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20was%20raped%20by%20a%20hotel%20porter%20while%20competing%20on%20the%20UK%20version%20of%20the%20show%20in%202012%20aged%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpraggan%2C%20who%20performed%20her%20own%20songs%20in%20her%20audition%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20X%20Factor%2C%26quot%3B%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20show%20during%20production%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.digitalspy.com%2Ftv%2Freality-tv%2Fa435432%2Flucy-spraggan-leaves-the-x-factor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eciting%20illness%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20real%20reason%20for%20her%20decision%20was%20because%20she'd%20been%20raped%2C%20she%20told%20The%20Guardian%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20incident%20occurred%20after%20a%20night%20out%20with%20her%20fellow%20contestant%20Rylan%20Clark%20and%20the%20show's%20producers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpraggan%20was%20dropped%20off%20at%20her%20hotel%20after%20they'd%20gone%20to%20a%20nightclub%2C%20and%20a%20porter%20took%20her%20to%20her%20room.%20She%20told%20the%20newspaper%20he%20later%20returned%20and%20assaulted%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20woke%20up%20the%20next%20day%20with%20this%20sense%20of%20sheer%20dread%2C%26quot%3B%20Spraggan%20told%20the%20Guardian.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20I've%20ever%20felt%20that%20level%20of%20confusion%20since.%20I%20knew%20that%20I'd%20been%20raped%2C%20but%20I%20could%20not%20process%20that.%20So%20I%20put%20my%20clothes%20on%20and%20went%20into%20autopilot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224644%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lucy%20Spraggan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b2ca23f9a25900194774de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223483%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELucy%20Spraggan%20at%20the%20DIVA%20Awards%20in%20London%20in%20April%202022.%3Cp%3ETim%20Whitby%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Fremantle%2C%20which%20produced%20%26quot%3BThe%20X%20Factor%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20the%20porter%20was%20later%20%26quot%3Bprosecuted%20and%20imprisoned%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20The%20Guardian%2C%20and%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20sorry%26quot%3B%20for%20Spraggan's%20ordeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20then%2C%20we%20have%20done%20our%20very%20best%20to%20learn%20lessons%20from%20these%20events%20and%20improve%20our%20aftercare%20processes%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20representative%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpraggan%20wasn't%20identified%20by%20the%20media%20due%20to%20UK%20laws%20preventing%20the%20identification%20of%20victims%20of%20sexual%20assault%2C%20but%20she%20waived%20her%20right%20to%20anonymity%20for%20the%20interview.%20It%20coincides%20with%20the%20publication%20on%20July%2020%20of%20her%20memoir%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBlinkPublishing%2F%3Flocale%3Den_GB%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProcess%3A%20Finding%20my%20way%20through%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpraggan%2C%20now%2031%2C%20told%20The%20Guardian%20she%20was%20offered%20no%20support%20from