ina%20was%20spending%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20developing%20%26quot%3Bethnic%20bioweapons%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20the%20US%20was%20also%20developing%20similar%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20origins%20of%20COVID-19%20are%20still%20unknown%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-57268111%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20hotly%20contested%20theory%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebeing%20that%20the%20virus%20might%20have%20escaped%20from%20a%20laboratory%20in%20Wuhan%2C%20China.%20Whether%20or%20not%20that%20theory%20is%20correct%2C%20there%20is%20no%20known%20evidence%20suggesting%20the%20virus%20was%20made%20to%20target%20specific%20ethnicities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy%20built%20a%20reputation%20as%20a%20prominent%20anti-vaxxer%20long%20before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20but%20his%20impact%20reached%20new%20heights%20when%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20began%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20report%20identified%20him%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobert-f-kennedy-jr-jfk-nephew-anti-vax-misinformation-facebook-2021-7%5C%22%3Ebeing%20one%20of%2012%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20were%20responsible%20for%20the%20spread%20of%20most%20disinformation%20about%20COVID-19%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20baselessly%20promoted%20a%20range%20of%20conspiracy%20theories%2C%20including%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-12215961%2FMark-Cuban-slams-Joe-Rogan-not-challenging-RFK-Jr-claims-WiFi-causes-cancer.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWi-Fi%20causes%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmtg-and-tucker-carlson-mass-shootings-ssris-antidepressants-explained-2022-7%5C%22%3Eantidepressants%20are%20to%20blame%20for%20school%20shootings.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20Kennedy%20dynasty%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%2