-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Flionel-messi-narrowly-escapes-car-crash-after-his-car-jumps-red-light-reports-4210984%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Flionel-messi-narrowly-escapes-car-crash-after-his-car-jumps-red-light-reports-4210984%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20And%20How%20Are%20CUET-UG%20Scores%20Normalised%3F%20Education%20Body%20Chief%20Explains%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20performance%20of%20every%20candidate%20in%20the%20Common%20University%20Entrance%20Test%20(CUET)-UG%20is%20evaluated%20using%20equi-percentile%20method%20and%20the%20marks%20reflected%20in%20the%20score%20card%20are%20normalised%20scores%2C%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(UGC)%20chief%20M%20Jagadesh%20Kumar%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20for%20CUET-UG%2C%20the%20gateway%20for%20undergraduate%20admissions%20to%20over%20200%20universities%20across%20the%20country%2C%20were%20announced%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20important%20to%20note%20is%20that%20CUET-UG%20has%20been%20conducted%20over%20a%20period%20of%20six%20weeks%20with%20tests%20in%20a%20given%20subject%20held%20on%20different%20days.%20So%20naturally%20the%20question%20that%20arises%20is%20how%20are%20we%20going%20to%20compare%20the%20performance%20of%20different%20students%20on%20a%20common%20scale%20since%20they%20have%20written%20the%20test%20in%20the%20same%20subject%20but%20on%20different%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kumar%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20admissions%20are%20made%20based%20on%20a%20score%20that%20accurately%20compares%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20why%20normalisation%20is%20done%20for%20CUET-UG%20and%20not%20all%20entrance%20exams%2C%20he%20said%20that%2C%20unlike%20CUET-UG%2C%20other%20entrance%20examinations%20are%20limited%20to%20fewer%20subjects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20single-session%20entrance%20tests%2C%20one%20common%20statistically%20established%20method%20is%20to%20transform%20the%20raw%20marks%20into%20a%20common%20uniform%20scale%20using%20the%20percentile%20method%20so%20that%20the%20performance%20of%20students%20can%20be%20compared%20to%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20UGC%20chief.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20in%20entrance%20tests%20such%20as%20CUET-UG%20since%20the%20test%20is%20conducted%20on%20different%20days%20and%20in%20multiple%20sessions%20for%20the%20same%20subject%2C%20it%20will%20give%20rise%20to%20multiple%20percentiles%20for%20each%20group%20of%20students.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20above%20difficulty%20another%20problem%20with%20using%20only%20percentiles%20is%20that%20in%20subjects%20such%20as%20Sports%20or%20Fine%20Arts%2C%20some%20weightage%20is%20given%20to%20the%20skill%20component%20by%20some%20universities%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%2C%20addition%20of%20raw%20marks%20in%20the%20skill%20component%20and%20the%20remaining%20weightage%20(75%20pc)%20of%20percentile%20cannot%20be%20done%20to%20prepare%20the%20rank%20list%20because%20it%20would%20be%20similar%20to%20adding%20oranges%20to%20apples%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20equi-percentile%20method%2C%20percentile%20for%20each%20candidate%20is%20calculated%20using%20the%20raw%20marks%20of%20the%20candidate%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20raw%20marks%20of%20others%20in%20the%20same%20session.%20This%20is%20done%20for%20every%20session%20across%20multiple%20days%20for%20the%20same%20subject.%20These%20percentiles%20are%20then%20equated%20and%20converted%20into%20normalised%20marks.%20For%20sessions%20with%20smaller%20number%20of%20candidates%2C%20these%20are%20clubbed%20with%20bigger%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20normalised%20marks%20of%20the%20candidates%2C%20obtained%20using%20equi-percentile%20method%2C%20in%20different%20sessions%20in%20a%20given%20subject%20can%20be%20used%20in%20the%20same%20way%20we%20use%20the%20raw%20marks%20of%20a%20conventional%20single%20session%20examination%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kumar%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20in%20a%20particular%20university%2C%20if%20the%20raw%20marks%20of%20the%20skill%20component%20has%20certain%20weightage%20it%20can%20be%20added%20to%20the%20remaining%20weightage%20of%20the%20normalised%20marks%20to%20prepare%20the%20rank%20list%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CUET-UG%20is%20the%20second-largest%20entrance%20exam%20in%20the%20country%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20number%20of%20applicants.%20In%20its%20first%20edition%2C%2012.5%20lakh%20students%20had%20registered%20for%20the%20exam%20and%209.9%20lakh%20had%20submitted%20their%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20edition%20of%20the%20crucial%20exam%20witnessed%20a%20remarkable%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20applications%2C%20with%20over%2014%20lakh%20students%20applying%20for%20the%20CUET-UG%2C%20a%2041%20per%20cent%20rise%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20this%20year's%20examination%20was%20conducted%20in%20three%20shifts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689435600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Fatiapkug_cbse-students-generic_625x300_22_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-and-how-are-cuet-ug-scores-normalised-education-body-chief-explains-4211035%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20performance%20of%20every%20candidate%20in%20the%20Common%20University%20Entrance%20Test%20(CUET)-UG%20is%20evaluated%20using%20equi-percentile%20method%20and%20the%20marks%20reflected%20in%20the%20score%20card%20are%20normalised%2