%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221413%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20person%20playing%20video%20games%20on%20a%20computer.%3Cp%3EMatei%20Alexandru%20Marcu%2FEyeEm%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EChildren%20addicted%20to%20video%20games%20run%20away%20from%20home%20in%20search%20of%20WiFi%20and%20turn%20violence%2C%20per%20a%20doctor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHenrietta%20Bowden-Jones%20heads%20up%20the%20UK's%20National%20Centre%20for%20Gaming%20Disorders.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInternet%20Gaming%20Disorder%20symptoms%20include%C2%A0loss%20of%20interest%20in%20other%20activities%20and%20using%20gaming%20to%20escape%20negative%20emotions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20young%20gamers%20are%20so%20addicted%20they%20resort%20to%20running%20away%20from%20home%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%20in%20search%20of%20an%20internet%20connection%20after%20theirs%20was%20cut%20off%20by%20a%20parent%2C%20according%20to%20an%20expert.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20UK%20clinic%20designed%20for%20treating%20video%20game%20addiction%2C%20originally%20expected%20to%20help%20just%2050%20people%20a%20year%2C%20has%20had%20more%20than%20850%20referrals%20since%20its%20inception%20in%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20met%20parents%20whose%20young%20children%20ran%20away%20from%20home%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%20to%20find%20WiFi%20on%20the%20steps%20of%20random%20homes%20when%20their%20own%20internet%20connection%20was%20switched%20off%20by%20parents%2C%26quot%3B%20Henrietta%20Bowden-Jones%2C%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Centre%20for%20Gaming%20Disorders%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fsociety%2F2023%2Fjul%2F14%2Fi-was-not-prepared-for-what-we-came-across-when-treating-gaming-disorders%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20in%20a%20first-person%20piece%20for%20the%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20met%20children%20who%20felt%20they%20would%20rather%20be%20dead%20than%20not%20game%20and%20said%20so%20to%20their%20parents.%20Things%20get%20broken%20in%20fits%20of%20rage.%20Sometimes%20people%20get%20hurt%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternet%20Gaming%20Disorder%20is%20defined%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fsdfe%2Fpdf%2Fdownload%2Feid%2F1-s2.0-S030646031730254X%2Ffirst-page-pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enine%20characteristics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20loss%20of%20interest%20in%20other%20activities%20and%20using%20gaming%20to%20escape%20negative%20emotions%2C%20five%20of%20which%20must%20be%20experienced%20with12%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBowden-Jones%20previously%20headed%20up%20the%20National%20Problem%20Gambling%20Clinic%20and%20became%20increasingly%20aware%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bcompulsive%20and%20destructive%20manner%26quot%3B%20children%20were%20spending%20money%20on%20games%2C%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20games%20involve%20loot%20boxes%2C%20typically%20unknown%20items%20unlocked%20through%20additional%20gameplay%20or%20paid%20for%20with%20real-world%20or%20in-game%20money.%20Video%20game%20companies%20EA%20and%20Respawn%20have%20faced%20criticism%20for%20expensive%20loot%20boxes%20in%20Apex%20Legends%2C%20with%20one%20axe%20totaling%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2019%2F08%2F15%2Fapex-legends-iron-crown-collection-axe-costs-least-136-microtransactions-10575671%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24178%20in%20microtransactions%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20it%20was%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20spend%20money%2C%20these%20children%20need%20to%20borrow%20money%20from%20parents%20or%20use%20monetary%20gifts%20received%20for%20birthdays%20and%20Christmas.%20The%20need%20for%20money%20is%20at%20the%20root%20of%20some%20of%20the%20domestic%20violence%20we%20see%2C%26quot%3B%20Bowden-Jones%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20no%20money%20is%20available%2C%20the%20most%20impulsive%20patients%20have%20stolen%20it%20by%20spending%20on%20their%20parents'%20bank%20cards.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20loot%20boxes%20count%20as%20gambling%20is%20a%20well-debated%20topic.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublications.parliament.uk%2Fpa%2Fcm201719%2Fcmselect%2Fcmcumeds%2F1846%2F1846.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUK%20digital%20and%20media%20committee%3C%2Fa%3E%20joined%20the%20Gambling%20Commission%20in%20calling%20games%20companies%20to%20do%20more%20to%20prevent%20in-game%20items%20from%20being%20traded%20for%20real-world%20money.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20then-Culture%20Secretary%20Nadine%20Dorries%20opted%20not%20to%20regulate%20loot%20boxes%20as%20gambling.%20An%20Austrian%20court%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2023%2F03%2F06%2Ffifa-loot-boxes-are-illegal-gambling-decides-austria-court-18392451%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecently%3C%2Fa%3E%20did%20the%20opposite%2C%20joining%20Belgium%20and%20Australia%20by%20imposing%20restrictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlmost%20no%20one%26quot%3B%20treated%20by%20the%20clinic%20has%20displayed%20both%20a%20gaming%20and%20gambling%20disorder%2C%20Bowden-Jones%20added.%20Still%2C%20research%20is%20needed%20on%20whether%20gamers%20develop%20gambling%20disorders%20laves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompetition%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20master%20a%20game%20are%20more%20important%20to%20younger%20patients%2C%20she%20wrote.%20Today%2C%20the%20doctor%20and%20a%20consultant%20psychiatrist%20treats%20everyone%2C%20from%20children%20to%20a%20woman%20in%20her%2070s.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchildren-addicted-video-games-ran-away-wifi-doctor-says-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22