working%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20who%20has%20implemented%20various%20welfare%20schemes%20and%20is%20credited%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20poverty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Fadnavis%20also%20listed%20various%20measures%20being%20implemented%20by%20the%20state%20government%20in%20the%20last%20year%20after%20coming%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20increased%20the%20honorarium%20of%20anganwadi%20workers%20and%20kotwals.%20We%20took%20decisions%20such%20as%20granting%20a%2050%20per%20cent%20concession%20to%20women%20in%20MSRTC%20bus%20travel%20and%20free%20travel%20to%20senior%20citizens%20(above%2075).%20I%20hope%20this%20government%20will%20fulfil%20all%20your%20expectations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Fadnavis%20invoked%20Lord%20Ram%20while%20speaking%20about%20the%20government%20programme%20as%20Nashik%20houses%20the%20famous%20temple%20of%20the%20deity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20has%20not%20come%20to%20your%20doorstep%20only%20but%20also%20in%20the%20court%20of%20Lord%20Ram.%20Nashik%20is%20a%20land%20of%20Kumbh%20Mela.%20This%20programme%20is%20a%20Kumbh%20Mela%20itself.%20It%20allows%20us%20to%20serve%20you%20as%20part%20of%20our%20effort%20to%20take%20the%20government%20to%20the%20last%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20this%2C%20some%20people%20have%20problems.%20To%20find%20a%20remedy%20to%20their%20problems%2C%20we%20brought%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20and%20now%20we%20have%20brought%20Ajit%20%3Cem%3Edada%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Pawar).%20Our%20government%20completed%20one%20year%20recently.%20In%20this%20period%2C%20we%20brought%20Maharashtra%20to%20the%20number%20one%20spot%20in%20investment%20and%20industries.%20This%20government%20has%20the%20faith%20of%20the%20country%20and%20the%20industrial%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20aid%20worth%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20has%20been