%20at%20the%20Australian%20Open%20and%20in%20Miami%2C%20and%20she%20had%20no%20answer%20to%20the%20big-hitting%20left-hander%20despite%20the%20support%20of%2015%2C000%20partisan%20fans%20on%20Centre%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20closed%20roof%2C%20Jabeur%20drew%20first%20blood%20with%20a%20break%20in%20the%20second%20game%20when%20Vondrousova%20netted%20a%20nervous%20backhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20immediately%20surrendered%20the%20initiative%20as%20Vondrousova%20broke%20back%20in%20the%20next%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJabeur's%20anxiety%20was%20clear%20as%20her%20unforced%20error%20total%20reached%20double%20figures%20in%20another%20wild%20game%20that%20gave%20Vondrousova%20a%205-4%20advantage%20that%20she%20gratefully%20seized%20to%20serve%20out%20the%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVondrousova%20made%20it%20five%20games%20in%20a%20row%20when%20Jabeur's%20weak%20forehand%20gifted%20her%20a%20break%20in%20the%20opening%20game%20of%20the%20second%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaking%20twice%20in%20three%20games%2C%20Jabeur%20moved%203-1%20up%2C%20only%20to%20falter%20again%20as%20the%20ninth%20break%20of%20the%20match%20allowed%20Vondrousova%20back%20into%20the%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20an%20opportunity%20the%20Czech%20was%20not%20going%20to%20spurn%20as%20Jabeur's%20unforced%20errors%20reached%2031%20by%20the%20final%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20Jabeur's%20meltdown%2C%20Vondrousova%20remained%20ice-cool%20and%20sealed%20her%20unexpected%20triumph%20with%20a%20perfect%20volley%20before%20falling%20to%20the%20turf%20in%20delight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689433260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F1edip32_saa_625x300_15_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwimbledon-2023%2Fmarketa-vondrousova-be