k.id%3Dd0e3151%26toc.depth%3D1%26toc.id%3D%26brand%3Ducpress%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elater%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BNow%20that%20the%20bomb%20could%20not%20be%20used%20against%20the%20Nazis%2C%20doubts%20arose.%20Those%20doubts%2C%20even%20if%20they%20do%20not%20appear%20in%20official%20reports%2C%20were%20discussed%20in%20many%20private%20conversations.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fahf.nuclearmuseum.org%2Fahf%2Fkey-documents%2Fszilard-petition%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efull%20petition%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Manhattan%20Project%20scientists%20and%20their%20names%20(provided%20by%20Szilard%20biographer%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dannen.com%2Fdecision%2F45-07-17.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Gene%20Dannen%3C%2Fa%3E)%20below.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20Manhattan%20Project%20petition%20asking%20President%20Truman%20not%20to%20bomb%20Japan%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20PETITION%20TO%20THE%20PRESIDENT%20OF%20THE%20UNITED%20STATES%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJuly%2017%2C%201945%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiscoveries%20of%20which%20the%20people%20of%20the%20United%20States%20are%20not%20aware%20may%20affect%20the%20welfare%20of%20this%20nation%20in%20the%20near%20future.%20The%20liberation%20of%20the%20atomic%20power%20which%20has%20been%20achieved%20places%20atomic%20bombs%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Army.%20It%20places%20in%20your%20hands%2C%20as%20Commander-in-Chief%2C%20the%20fateful%20decision%20whether%20or%20not%20to%20sanction%20the%20use%20of%20such%20bombs%20in%20the%20present%20phase%20of%20the%20war%20against%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%2C%20the%20undersigned%20scientists%2C%20have%20been%20working%20in%20the%20field%20of%20atomic%20power.%20Until%20recently%20we%20have%20had%20to%20fear%20that%20the%20United%20States%20might%20be%20attacked%20by%20atomic%20bombs%20during%20this%20war%20and%20that%20her%20only%20defense%20might%20lie%20in%20a%20counterattack%20by%20the%20same%20means.%20Today%2C%20with%20the%20defeat%20of%20Germany%2C%20this%20danger%20is%20averted%20and%20we%20feel%20impelled%20to%20say%20what%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20has%20to%20be%20brought%20speedily%20to%20a%20successful%20conclusion%20and%20attacks%20by%20atomic%20bombs%20may%20very%20well%20be%20an%20effective%20method%20of%20warfare.%20We%20feel%2C%20however%2C%20that%20such%20attacks%20on%20Japan%20could%20not%20be%20justified%2C%20at%20least%20not%20until%20the%20terms%20which%20will%20be%20imposed%20after%20the%20war%20on%20Japan%20were%20made%20public%20in%20detail%20and%20Japan%20were%20given%20an%20opportunity%20to%20surrender.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20such%20public%20announcement%20gave%20assurance%20to%20the%20Japanese%20that%20they%20could%20look%20forward%20to%20a%20life%20devoted%20to%20peaceful%20pursuit%20in%20their%20homeland%20and%20if%20Japan%20still%20refused%20to%20surrender%2C%20our%20nation%20might%20then%2C%20in%20certain%20circumstances%2C%20find%20itself%20forced%20to%20resort%20to%20the%20use%20of%20atomic%20bombs.%20Such%20a%20step%2C%20however%2C%20ought%20not%20to%20be%20made%20at%20any%20time%20without%20seriously%20considering%20the%20moral%20responsibilities%20which%20are%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20of%20atomic%20power%20will%20provide%20the%20nations%20with%20new%20means%20of%20destruction.%20The%20atomic%20bombs%20at%20our%20disposal%20represent%20only%20the%20first%20step%20in%20this%20direction%2C%20and%20there%20is%20almost%20no%20limit%20to%20the%20destructive%20power%20which%20will%20become%20available%20in%20the%20course%20of%20their%20future%20development.%20Thus%20a%20nation%20which%20sets%20the%20precedent%20of%20using%20these%20newly%20liberated%20forces%20of%20nature%20for%20purposes%20of%20destruction%20may%20have%20to%20bear%20the%20responsibility%20of%20opening%20the%20door%20to%20an%20era%20of%20devastation%20on%20an%20unimaginable%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20after%20the%20war%20a%20situation%20is%20allowed%20to%20develop%20in%20the%20world%20which%20permits%20rival%20powers%20to%20be%20in%20uncontrolled%20possession%20of%20these%20new%20means%20of%20destruction%2C%20the%20cities%20of%20the%20United%20States%20as%20well%20as%20the%20cities%20of%20other%20nations%20will%20be%20in%20continuous%20danger%20of%20sudden%20annihilation.%20All%20the%20resources%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20moral%20and%20material%2C%20may%20have%20to%20be%20mobilized%20to%20prevent%20the%20advent%20of%20such%20a%20world%20situation.%20Its%20prevention%20is%20at%20present%20the%20solemn%20responsibility%20of%20the%20United%20States%E2%80%94singled%20out%20by%20virtue%20of%20her%20lead%20in%20the%20field%20of%20atomic%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20added%20material%20strength%20which%20this%20lead%20gives%20to%20the%20United%20States%20brings%20with%20it%20the%20obligation%20of%20restraint%20and%20if%20we%20were%20to%20violate%20this%20obligation%20our%20moral%20position%20would%20be%20weakened%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20world%20and%20in%20our%20own%20eyes.%20It%20would%20then%20be%20more%20difficult%20for%20us%20to%20live%20up%20to%20our%20responsibility%20of%20bringing%20the%20unloosened%20forces%20of%20destruction%20under%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20view%20of%20the%20foregoing%2C%20we%2C%20the%20undersigned%2C%20respectfully%20petition%3A%20first%2C%20that%20you%20exercise%20your%20power%20as%20Commander-in-Chief%2C%20to%20rule%20that%20the%20United%20States%20shall%20not%20resort%20to%20the%20use%20of%20atomic%20bombs%20in%20this%20war%20unless%20the%20terms%20which%20will%20be%20imposed%20upon%20Japan%20have%20been%20made%20public%20in%20detail%20and%20Japan%20knowing%20these%20terms%20has%20refused%20to%20surrender%3B%20second%2C%20that%20in%20such%20an%20event%20the%20question%20whether%20or%20not%20to%20use%20atomic%20bombs%20be%20decided%20by%20you%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20consideration%2