m%2Fkentucky-man-finds-700-civil-war-coins-buried-farm-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689430393000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b15c4bf9a259001947546e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkentucky-man-finds-700-civil-war-coins-buried-farm-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20US%20coins%20expert%20said%20the%20discovery%20of%20700%20Civil%20War-era%20gold%20coins%20%26quot%3Bcannot%20be%20overstated.%26quot%3B%20The%20trove%20has%20been%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3BGreat%20Kentucky%20Hoard.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ashoaib%40insider.com%20(Alia%20Shoaib)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A64%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkentucky-man-finds-700-civil-war-coins-buried-farm-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Same%20As%20Jaiswal...%5C%22%3A%20Ponting%20On%20Star%20Who%20Did%20Not%20Get%20Chance%20In%20WI%20Test%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAustralia%20great%20Ricky%20Ponting%20has%20identified%20a%20group%20of%20young%20India%20batters%20that%20can%20match%20the%20exploits%20of%20opener%20Yashavi%20Jaiswal%20and%20prosper%20at%20Test%20level%20if%20given%20the%20chance%20during%20the%20new%20ICC%20World%20Test%20Championship%20cycle.%20Jaiswal%20was%20one%20of%20two%20players%20given%20Test%20debuts%20for%20India%20in%20the%20present%20Test%20against%20the%20West%20Indies%20in%20Dominica%2C%20and%20the%2021-year-old%20quickly%20proved%20he%20was%20up%20to%20the%20task%2C%20becoming%20only%20the%2017th%20Indian%20player%20to%20make%20a%20century%20on%20Test%20debut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20speaking%20on%20the%20most%20recent%20episode%20of%20The%20ICC%20Review%2C%20Ponting%20was%20full%20of%20praise%20for%20Jaiswal%2C%20admitting%20that%20he%20was%20not%20surprised%20to%20see%20the%20left-hander%20make%20a%20strong%20impression%20after%20seeing%20him%20amass%20625%20runs%20for%20the%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20during%20the%20most%20recent%20season%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20mean%20(Yashasvi)%20Jaiswal's%20IPL%20was%20something%20special.%20He%20almost%20just%20flicked%20a%20switch%20and%20turned%20into%20a%20superstar%20overnight.%20Everyone%20knew%20that%20he%20was%20a%20talented%20youngster%2C%20but%20what%20I%20saw%20in%20this%20year's%20IPL%2C%20he's%20got%20all%20sorts%20of%20talent%2C%26quot%3B%20Ponting%20told%20ICC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPonting%20believes%20a%20slew%20of%20other%20uncapped%20youngsters%20will%20be%20inspired%20by%20Jaiswal%20and%20perform%20similarly%20if%20given%20a%20chance%20at%20Test%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPonting%20nominated%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20-%20who%20scored%20590%20runs%20during%20this%20year's%20IPL%20and%20is%20also%20in%20India's%20touring%20party%20currently%20in%20the%20Caribbean%20-%20as%20another%20player%20who%20may%20shine%20in%20the%20coming%20years%20and%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20and%20Prithvi%20Shaw%20as%20two%20other%20batters%20that%20could%20easily%20adjust%20quickly%20to%20the%20rigours%20of%20Test%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20those%20young%20Indian%20guys%20that%20I%20can't%20wait%20to%20see%20play%20Test%20cricket%20and%20yet%20you%20look%20at%20their%20domestic%20records%20as%20well%20and%20you%20can't%20help%20but%20be%20impressed.%20I'm%20on%20record%20saying%20that%20I%20think%20(Ruturaj)%20Gaikwad's%20the%20same%20(as%20Jaiswal).%20I%20think%20he%20could%20be%20a%20very%20serious%20Test%20match%20player%20or%20all-format%20player%20really%20in%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Ponting%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaw%20is%20another%20player%20who%20Ponting%20believes%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20flourish%20for%20India%20in%20the%20future%20if%20he%20works%20hard%20to%20make%20a%20comeback.%20Shaw%20made%20his%20international%20debut%20in%202018%2C%20but%20has%20not%20re