20the%20pilot%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.popularmechanics.com%2Ftechnology%2Finfrastructure%2Fg2021%2Fhistory-of-flying-car%2F%5C%22%3EPopular%20Mechanics%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20not%20all%20attempts%20at%20flying%20cars%20were%20so%20lucky.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222222%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20AVE%20Mizar%20taking%20flight%20on%20an%20airport%20runway%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F649b37876eb0a800194d61b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20AVE%20Mizar%20taking%20flight%20on%20an%20airport%20runway.%3Cp%3EBettmann%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201971%2C%20Henry%20Smolinski%20and%20Harold%20Blake%20died%20when%20their%20flying%20car%20prototype%20crashed%20and%20exploded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20engineers%20from%20California%20were%20taking%20their%20car%20on%20a%20test%20flight%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finventors-killed-by-died-from-their-own-inventions-2023-6%23henry-smolinski-and-harold-blake-6%5C%22%3Ewhen%20black%20smoke%20began%20emanating%20from%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20car%20crashed%2C%20and%20the%20two%20died%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThese%20real-life%20failures%20didn't%20stop%20Hollywood%20from%20imagining%20flying%20cars.%20This%20time%2C%20they%20were%20more%20than%20just%20cars%20with%20wings%20attached.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222230%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20'Spinner'%20flying%20car%20takes%20off%20in%20a%20scene%20from%20Ridley%20Scott's%20futuristic%20thriller%20'Blade%20Runner'%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64aee72a94be880019f3a320%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221673%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20'Spinner'%20flying%20car%20takes%20off%20in%20a%20scene%20from%20Ridley%20Scott's%20futuristic%20thriller%20'Blade%20Runner'%3Cp%3EWarner%20Bro