20BJP%20plays%20out%20the%20politics%20around%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20inauguration%20and%20public%20sentiment%20over%20economic%20issues.%20But%20it%20would%20also%20depend%20significantly%20on%20how%20the%20Left-Congress%20combine%20manages%20to%20posit%20themselves%20as%20the%20real%20ideological%20opponent%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20as%20there%20is%20a%20clear%20indication%20of%20triangular%20contests%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhattacharyya%20told%20The%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689425028000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15180344%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-08-at-11.11.35-AM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbengal-panchayat-election-left-bjp%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lok%20Sabha-wise%20analysis%20of%20panchayat%20and%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20civic%20polls%20show%20the%20Left-Congress%20vote%20share%20coming%20uncomfortably%20close%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbengal-panchayat-election-left-bjp%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Welcome%20to%20the%20future%20of%20America%3A%20a%20chicken%20in%20every%20pot%20and%20a%20pro%20sports%20team%20in%20every%20backyard%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Austin%20FC%20supporters.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b181e39751e300192a260a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221645%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESupporters%20for%20the%20new%20MLS%20club%20in%20Austin%2C%20TX.%3Cp%3ESasha%20Haagensen%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Heineken%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBig%20players%20like%20the%20NBA%20and%20MLB%20are%20eyeing%20expansion.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMLS%20has%20added%20several%20new%20teams%20already%2C%20and%20more%20are%20coming.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMore%20league