et%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b166c9f9a25900194757fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20DSP%20driver%20said%20that%20his%20company%20provides%20drivers%20with%20bungee%20cords%20to%20keep%20Amazon%20Prime%20packages%20in%20place%20during%20the%20Prime%20season.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20DSP%20driver%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20had%20way%20more%20totes%20that%20have%20packages%20in%20them.%20There's%20different%20ways%20of%20loading%20our%20vans%2C%20and%20they're%20encouraging%20us%20to%20triple-stack%20the%20totes.%20So%20there's%20a%20vertical%20column%20of%20three%20in%20a%20cargo%20van%20and%20that's%20kind%20of%20messy%20unless%20there's%20a%20way%20to%20restrain%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20they%20supplied%20us%20with%20bungee%20cords%20so%20we%20can%20lash%20the%20totes%20to%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20van%20so%20the%20totes%20don't%20tip%20over%20while%20you're%20driving.%20They%20gave%20us%20those%20tools%2C%20at%20least%2C%20to%20make%20it%20a%20little%20bit%20easier%20with%20all%20the%20increased%20packages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20it's%20as%20bad%20as%20it%20could%20be%2C%20but%20I%20mean%2C%20I'm%20just%20speaking%20for%20myself.%20For%20other%20people%20it%20might%20be%20worse%3A%20more%20stops%2C%20more%20locations%2C%20more%20packages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20try%20to%20take%20care%20of%20myself%20by%20taking%20breaks%2C%20staying%20hydrated%2C%20and%20taking%20ibuprofen%20and%20Tylenol%20for%20my%20body%20aches%20but%20the%20work%20is%20draining%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20gotten%20busier%20and%20it's%20really%20hot%20and%20humid.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20AC%20but%20we're%20not%20allowed%20to%20run%20the%20engines%20during%20stops.%20So%20whenever%20we%20turn%20off%20the%20engine%2C%20get%20the%20package%2C%20bring%20it%20to%20the%20door%20and%20go%20back%20to%20the%20van%2C%20it's