%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EAll%20references%20to%20a%20Memorandum%20of%20Understanding%20for%20three%20Scorpene-class%20submarines%20were%20removed%20from%20a%20later%20version%20of%20the%20India-France%20bilateral%20document%20on%20the%20future%20roadmap%20of%20ties.%20This%20MoU%20had%20been%20mentioned%20in%20an%20earlier%20version%20of%20the%20uploaded%20text.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOfficial%20sources%20claimed%20that%20the%20previous%20document%20was%20not%20the%20approved%20text%20and%20%E2%80%9Csome%20earlier%20negotiating%20text%20got%20uploaded.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fdefence-ties-serve-as-the-basic-pillar-of-india-france-bilateral-relations-modi%5C%22%3Eabsence%20of%20any%20Rafale%20jet%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20roadmap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20delegation-level%20talks%20between%20Indian%20and%20French%20leaders%20in%20Paris%20on%20Friday%2C%20July%2014%2C%20a%20slew%20of%20diplomatic%20documents%20were%20issued%20by%20both%20sides.%20The%20joint%20communique%20was%20a%20short%20text%2C%20with%20the%20substantial%20document%20being%20the%20%E2%80%98Horizon%202047%20%E2%80%93%2025th%20Anniversary%20of%20the%20India-France%20Strategic%20Partnership%2C%20Towards%20A%20Century%20of%20India-France%20Relations%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBased%20on%20the%20uploaded%20Horizon%202047%20document%20on%20the%20MEA%E2%80%99s%20website%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20other%20Indian%20media%20outlets%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fdefence-ties-serve-as-the-basic-pillar-of-india-france-bilateral-relations-modi%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported%20that%20there%20was%20an%20absence%20of%20the%20expected%20deal%20for%20purchasing%2026%20additional%20Rafale%20fighter%20jets%20for%20the%20Indian%20Navy.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%2C%20the%20text%20also%20had%20mentioned%20that%20India%20and%20France%20%E2%80%9Cwelcome%20the%20MoU%20between%20Mazgon%20Dockyard%20Ltd%20and%20Naval%20Group%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20three%20additional%20submarines%20under%20the%20P75%20programme%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20the%20deals%20had%20been%20approved%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20Defence%20Acquisition%20Council%20and%20announced%20by%20the%20Indian%20defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20on%20his%20Twitter%20account%20a%20day%20earlier%20on%20Thursday.%20While%20the%20price%20was%20still%20to%20be%20negotiated%2C%20the%20total%20cost%20of%20both%20the%20deals%20was%20estimated%20around%20%249.5%20billion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20on%20Saturday%20morning%2C%20India%20time%2C%20the%20line%20about%20the%20MoU%20for%20the%20three%20additional%20submarines%20had%20disappeared.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwebcache.googleusercontent.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dcache%3Ahttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fbilateral-documents.htm%3Fdtl%2F36806%2FHorizon_2047_25th_Anniversary_of_the_IndiaFrance_Strategic_Partnership_Towards_A_Century_of_IndiaFrance_Relations%26sxsrf%3DAB5stBjcMGapLWK7Gy_VnU3IFmF6pTHO0Q%3A1689419641736%26source%3Dhp%26ei%3DeX-yZLSpKpjt2roPuP6KmAI%26iflsig%3DAD69kcEAAAAAZLKNiRQ-nM0jl-o3mQOhmtr3TVeUGcST%26ved%3D0ahUKEwj0yfrMypCAAxWYtlYBHTi_AiMQ4dUDCAk%26uact%3D5%26oq%3Dcache%3Ahttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fbilateral-documents.htm%3Fdtl%2F36806%2FHorizon_2047_25th_Anniversary_of_the_IndiaFrance_Strategic_Partnership_Towards_A_Century_of_IndiaFrance_Relations%26gs_lp%%26sclient%3Dgws-wiz%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20cached%20version%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20earlier%20uploaded%20text%20shows%20the%20difference.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-capt