try.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A46%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-asia-66209886%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Backstory%3A%20Revisiting%20the%20Ruins%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Media%20Ahead%20of%20the%20Fourth%20Anniversary%20of%20August%205%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15152028%2FUntitled-design-20-1-e1689414652592.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fit-rules-amendment-legal-complications%5C%22%3Etweak%20its%20Information%20Technology%20Rules%2C%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20allow%20it%20to%20label%20media%20reports%20relating%20to%20the%20government%20as%20%E2%80%9Cfalse%E2%80%9D%20has%20created%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20public%20outrage%20and%20judicial%20scrutiny.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20this%20experiment%20in%20state%20censorship%20is%20not%20new.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20June%202%2C%202020%2C%20the%20administration%20of%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20introduced%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fkashmir-new-media-policy-press-freedom%5C%22%3Emedia%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20that%20allowed%20it%20to%20examine%20the%20content%20of%20print%2C%20electronic%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20media%20for%20%E2%80%9Cfake%20news%2C%20plagiarism%20and%20unethical%20or%20anti-national%20content%E2%80%9D%20and%20order%20its%20take%20down.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20for%20good%20reason%20they%20say%20that%20if%20the%20security%20apparatus%20in%20Kashmir%20sneezes%20today%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20will%20get%20a%20cold%20later.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnderstanding%20the%20experiments%20%E2%80%93%20and%20I%20will%20confine%20myself%20to%20those%20involving%20the%20media%20%E2%80%93%20being%20conducted%20in%20that%20laboratory%20called%20Kashmir%2C%20where%20the%20lab%20technicians%20wear%20jackboots%2C%20is%20exceedingly%20important%20if%20we%20are%20to%20have%20a%20better%20sense%20of%C2%A0%20the%20trajectories%20that%20are%20generally%20favoured%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20present%20juncture%20is%20particularly%20apposite%20to%20revisit%20this%20theme.%20India%20will%20soon%20be%20marking%20the%20fifth%20anniversary%20of%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20finally%20sitting%20down%20to%20hear%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20constitutionality%20of%20the%20move%20(%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-article-370-kashmir-jammu%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNew%2520Delhi%253A%2520The%2520Supreme%2520Court%2527s%2Cunion%2520territories%2520of%2520Ladakh%2520and%5C%22%3EArticle%20370%3A%20SC%20to%20Disregard%20Union%20Govt%E2%80%99s%20Fresh%20Affidavit%2C%20Draws%20Roadmap%20for%20Hearing%20Challenges%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20July%2011)%20after%20snubbing%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20in%20filing%20a%20fresh%20affidavit%20with%20the%20apparent%20intent%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20the%20core%20issue%20of%20constitutionalism%20(%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-narendra-modi-article-370%23%3A~%3Atext%3Dto%2520National%2520Politics-%2CArticle%2520370%253A%2520SC%2520Rebuffs%2520Modi%2520Government%2520in%2520a%2520Case%2CGreat%2520Significance%2520to%2520National%2520Politics%26amp%3Btext%3DThe%2520court%2520has%2520made%2520it%2Cwas%2520constitutionally%2520tenable%2520or%2520not.%5C%22%3EArticle%20370%3A%20SC%20Rebuffs%20Modi%20Government%20in%20a%20Case%20of%20Great%20Significance%20to%20National%20Politics%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20July%2011).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20management%20of%20the%20media%20was%20one%20of%20the%20central%20planks%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20policy-making%20on%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemember%20those%20fraught%20days%20just%20before%20and%20after%20the%20reading%20down%20four%20years%20ago%3F%20A%20combination%20of%20media%20manipulation%20and%20military%20mobilisation%20marked%20those%20early%20days.%20As%20additional%20reinforcements%20of%20security%20forces%20were%20marched%20in%20to%20complement%20the%20estimated%20700%2C000%20Indian%20armed%20personnel%20permanently%20stationed%20in%20Kashmir%20(and%20this%20may%20be%20a%20gross%20underestimation)%2C%20there%20was%20a%20media%20gag%20so%20impenetrable%2C%20so%20sudden%2C%20so%20cynical%2C%20so%20ruthless%2C%20that%20the%20entire%20region%20was%20blindsided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20on%20August%204%2C%202019%2C%20news%20of%20the%20arrests%20of%20political%20leaders%20came%20in%20and%20as%20local%20journalists%20scrambled%20to%20file%20news%20reports%20on%20this%2C%20the%20internet%20started%20fading%20out%20and%20by%2012.30%20am%2C%20according%20to%20local%20accounts%2C%20was%20non-functional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20television%20screens%20yielded%20little%20but%20static%20and%20phone%20lines%2C%20including%20that%20old%20faithful%20%E2%80%93%20the%20landline%20%E2%80%93%20went%20dead.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.himalmag.com%2Fmilitarisation-and-the-media%2F%5C%22%3EAs%20I%20had%20written%20in%20a%20piece%20at%20that%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20this%20happened%20in%20the%20hours%20before%20dawn%20without%20any%20prior%20intimation%20or%20formal%20public%20orders.%20By%20daybreak%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20to%20every%20Kashmiri%20that%20beyond%20her%20or%20his%20capacity%20to%20physically%20communicate%20with%20family%20members%20and%20neighbours%20in%20the%20immediate%20vicinity%2C%20she%20or%20he%20stood%20isolated%20and%20alone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20journalists%2C%20this%20also%20meant%20the%20sudden%20death%20of%20their%20professional%20identity.%20They%20were%20now%20running%20around%20for%20curfew%20passes%20and%20%E2%80%98movement%20passes%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%20Newspapers%20that%20had%20somehow%20scrambled%20up%20a%20couple%20of%20pages%20%E2%80%93%20most%20carrying%20sad%20advertisements%20about%20the%20cancellation%20of%20marriages%20%E2%80%93%20discovered%20that%20hurdles%20were%20being%20placed%20on%20their%20distribution%20networks.%20The%20message%20was%20clear.%20Kashmir%20was%20to%20be%20completely%20fire-walled%20as%20a%20discursive%20space%20and%20public%20sphere.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20her%20recent%20book%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Dismantled%20State%20The%20Story%20of%20Kashmir%20After%20Article%20370%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Anuradha%20Bhasin%2C%20executive%20editor%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20put%20it%20succinctly%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%205%20August%202019%20did%20was%20to%20freeze%20the%20media%20by%20insulating%20Kashmir%20inside%20out.%20Both%20journalists%20and%20journalism%20disappeared.%E2%80%9D%20She%20goes%20on%20to%20say%20that%20soon%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Esummons%20to%20journalists%20and%20their%20repeated%20harassment%20and%20interrogation%20by%20the%20police%20became%20routine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20exact%20count%20of%20the%20journalists%20who%20have%20faced%20the%20wrath%20of%20the%20police%20at%20the%20counter-insurgency%20centre%20%E2%80%98Cargo%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20at%20least%20three%20dozen%20cases%20have%20come%20to%20light.%20The%20numbers%20may%20be%20higher%20but%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20admit%20publicly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20singular%20attempt%20of%20the%20Indian%20state%20was%20to%20dominate%20the%20narrative%20on%20Kashmir.%20Initially%20it%20was%20about%20suppressing%20any%20information%20on%20public%20anger%20and%20resistance%20to%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%2C%20even%20as%20reports%20generated%20by%20the%20national%20media%2C%20supported%2C%20celebrated%20and%20eulogised%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20actions%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20celebratory%20%E2%80%98Kashmir-is-ours%E2%80%99%20trope%20manifested%20itself%20in%20prime%20time%20coverage%20and%20social%20media%20posts%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%23370goes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20went%20viral.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20denied%20outright%20that%20the%20media%20in%20the%20state%20was%20being%20gagged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Prakash%20Javadekar%2C%20the%20then%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EUnion%20Minister%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ewas%20questioned%20by%20the%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eabout%20the%20lack%20of%20media%20freedom%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20he%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20true.%20Doordarshan%20is%20working.%20Akashvani%20is%20being%20broadcast%20in%20all%20languages.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20efforts%20were%20now%20made%20to%20promote%20the%20idea%20that%20Kashmir%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpeaceful%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20whole%20exercise%20in%20reading%20down%20Article%20370%20was%20a%20resounding%20success.%20A%20little%20tour%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20A.%20S.%20Doval%20took%20through%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmilitancy%20prone%E2%80%9D%20area%20in%20the%20state%20was%20prominently%20showcased%20on%20national%20media%20as%20evidence%20of%20this.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20newly%20declared%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20under%20what%20became%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20longest%20internet%20blackout%20that%20lasted%20from%20August%202019%20to%20January%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F05154400%2FSrinagar-article-370-security-curfew2020_8img05_Aug_2020_PTI05-08-2020_000098B.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F05154400%2FSrinagar-article-370-security-curfew2020_8img05_Aug_2020_PTI05-08-2020_000098B.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F05154400%2FSrinagar-article-370-security-curfew2020_8img05_Aug_2020_PTI05-08-2020_000098B-300x195.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F05154400%2FSrinagar-article-370-security-curfew2020_8img05_Aug_2020_PTI05-08-2020_000098B-1024x666.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-471377%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFile%20Photo.%20Security%20personnel%20stand%20guard%20on%20a%20street%20during%20restrictions%20imposed%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20first%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Article%20370%20move%2C%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20Wednesday%2C%20Aug.%205%2C%202020.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20%E2%80%9Cpeace%E2%80%9D%20was%20supposedly%20established%2C%20the%20next%20phase%20demanded%20hyping%20up%20the%20perception%20of%20%E2%80%9Cnormalcy%E2%80%9D.%20The%20effort%20carries%20on%20to%20the%20present%20day.%20When%20delegates%20gathered%20at%20Srinagar%20for%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E3rd%20G20%20Tourism%20Working%20Group%20Meeting%20this%20May%2C%20so%20anxious%20were%20the%20authorities%20to%20present%20an%20idyllic%20%E2%80%9Cnormalcy%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20state%2C%C2%A0%20that%20police%20outposts%20were%20covered%20by%20boards%20that%20welcomed%20delegates%20and%20shopkeepers%20were%20made%20to%20keep%20their%20establishments%20open%20beyond%20working%20hours.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ET%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20government%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdilution-of-article-370-brought-unprecedented-progress-and-security-to-jk-centre-tells-sc%5C%22%3Erecent%20affidavit%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20indicates%20how%20important%20this%20projection%20of%20%E2%80%9Cnormalcy%E2%80%9D%20is%20for%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20in%20Kashmir.%20It%20claimed%20that%20protests%3B%20bandhs%2C%20stone%20pelting%20incidents%2C%20no%20longer%20take%20place%3B%20that%20schools%20and%20universities%20are%20functioning%20normally%2C%20with%20students%20participating%20in%20large%20numbers%20in%20sporting%20activities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Flife-normal-peace-ascendant-and-stones-silent-in-kashmir-union-government-affidavit-tells-supreme-court-on-eve-of-article-370-hearings%2F%5C%22%3EThere%20is%20a%20particularly%20significant%20observation%20also%20made%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CResolute%20anti-terror%20actions%20have%20resulted%20in%20the%20dismantling%20of%20the%20terror%20eco-system%20which%20is%20reflected%20in%20a%20significant%20drop%20in%20terrorist%20recruitment%20from%20199%20in%20the%20year%202018%20to%2012%20in%20the%20year%202023%20till%20date.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManaging%20the%20media%2C%20it%20appears%2C%20is%20part%20of%20what%20the%20government%20terms%20are%20%E2%80%9Cresolute%20anti-terror%20actions%E2%80%9D.%20The%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20has%20undertaken%20various%20measures%20designed%20to%20intimidate%20the%20media%2C%20including%20the%20widespread%20use%20of%20terror%20laws%20to%20incarcerate%20journalists%20and%20the%20forcibly%20takeover%20of%20the%20Srinagar%20Press%20Club.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20normalcy%20is%20defined%20as%20the%20choking%20of%20all%20independent%20information%20flows%3B%20of%20gagging%20media%20outlets%3B%20terrorising%20people%20into%20silence%20through%20threats%2C%20surveillance%20and%20random%20arrests%3B%20suspending%20the%20internet%20at%20will%20(in%202022%2C%20the%20internet%20went%20on%20the%20blink%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20no%20less%20than%2024%20times)%20and%20failure%20to%20conduct%20elections%20for%20years%20on%20end%2C%20then%20normalcy%20has%20indeed%20been%20established%20in%20Kashmir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EQuestion%20though%20is%20whether%20such%20%E2%80%9Cnormalcy%E2%80%9D%20can%20be%20classified%20as%20democracy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20vulnerability%20of%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20journalists%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELate%20on%20the%20night%20of%20July%208%2C%20senior%20Pakistani%20journalist%2C%20Syed%20Muhammad%20Askari%2C%20working%20for%20the%20Karachi-based%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDaily%20Jang%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20was%20spirited%20away%20by%20police%20accompanied%20by%20plainclothes%20personnel%2C%20from%20a%20location%20near%20the%20Qayyumabad%20KPT%20Interchange%20on%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20Korangi%20Road.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20disappearance%20sent%20alarm%20bells%20ringing%2C%20not%20just%20in%20Pakistan%20but%20across%20south%20Asia%2C%20because%20stories%20of%20such%20disappearances%20have%20sometimes%20ended%20very%20badly.%20In%20May%202011%2C%20there%20was%20the%20tragic%20case%20of%20Saleem%20Shahzad%2C%20who%20worked%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAsia%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20Hong%20Kong-based%20online%20portal.%20Two%20days%20later%2C%20his%20corpse%20surfaced%20on%20the%20bank%20of%20a%20canal%20and%20it%20bore%20visible%20signs%20of%20torture%2C%20indicative%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20Shahzad%20had%20made%20some%20powerful%20enemies%20in%20the%20top%20echelons%20of%20the%20Inter-Service%20Intelligence.%20He%20had%20evidently%20broken%20an%20unspoken%20rule%20%E2%80%93%20attack%20the%20government%20all%20you%20want%2C%20but%20never%20attack%20the%20military%20apparatus.%20One%20of%20his%20stories%20had%20evidently%20revealed%20the%20involvement%20of%20a%20group%20of%20naval%20officers%20with%20the%20al%20Qaeda%20and%20he%20paid%20the%20price%20for%20it%20with%20his%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20recently%2C%20there%20was%20the%20case%20of%20Arshad%20Sharif.%20The%2049-year-old%20was%20known%20for%20his%20investigative%20reportage%2C%20but%20he%20was%20also%20an%20experienced%20broadcaster%2C%20having%20worked%20for%20prominent%20Pakistani%20news%20channels%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDawn%20News%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAAJNews%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EARY%20TV%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Sharif%20was%20shot%20dead%20last%20October%20in%20Nairobi%2C%20Kenya%2C%20to%20where%20he%20had%20fled%20to%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20save%20his%20life.%20He%20too%20had%20a%20string%20of%20exposes%20of%20corruption%20in%20the%20highest%20echelons%20of%20the%20military%20establishment%20to%20his%20credit.%20He%20too%20was%20said%20to%20be%20brutally%20tortured%20before%20being%20shot%20dead.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPakistan%20has%20a%20well-deserved%20reputation%20of%20being%20a%20dangerous%20place%20to%20practice%20journalism.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20International%20Federation%20of%20Journalists%20rates%20it%20as%20the%20fifth%20most%20deadly%20in%20the%20world%20and%20the%20treatment%20accorded%20to%20them%20range%20from%20enforced%20disappearances%20and%20kidnappings%20to%C2%A0%20imprisonment%20and%20torture.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20point%20to%20note%20here%20is%20that%20even%20fleeing%20to%20another%20country%20cannot%20guarantee%20protection.%20As%20another%20journalist%2C%20Taha%20Siddiqui%2C%20who%20has%20presently%20taken%20refuge%20in%20France%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fopinions%2F2019%2F01%2F08%2Fim-journalist-who-fled-pakistan-i-no-longer-feel-safe-exile%2F%5C%22%3Eexplained%20in%20a%20searing%20piece%20he%20wrote%20in%202019%20for%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fopinions%2F2019%2F01%2F08%2Fim-journalist-who-fled-pakistan-i-no-longer-feel-safe-exile%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20began%3A%20%E2%80%9COn%20Jan.%2010%2C%202018%2C%20I%20survived%20an%20abduction%20and%20possible%20assassination%20attempt%20by%20armed%20men%20who%20stopped%20my%20taxi%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20highway%20in%20Islamabad%E2%80%A6Luckily%2C%20I%20escaped.%20I%20believe%20the%20attack%20was%20orchestrated%20by%20the%20Pakistani%20army%2C%20which%20has%20been%20threatening%20me%20for%20years%20over%20my%20journalistic%20work%20on%20military%20abuses%20in%20Pakistan.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20forced%20Siddiqui%20to%20flee%20but%20he%20has%20been%20advised%20that%20should%20he%20continue%20exposing%20the%20ways%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Army%2C%20they%20will%20continue%20to%20come%20for%20him%3A%20%E2%80%9CEven%20in%20exile%2C%20I%20feel%20unsafe%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20revealed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20these%20manifest%20dangers%2C%20either%20de%20facto%20or%20de%20jure%2C%20from%20those%20who%20rule%2C%20Pakistan%20has%20seen%20a%20flourishing%20of%20independent%20journalism.%20Towering%20figures%20like%20the%20poet%2C%20Faiz%20Ahmed%20Faiz%2C%20have%20left%20their%20stamp%20on%20its%20legacy.%20Faiz%20helped%20to%20establish%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPakistan%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20turbulent%20period%20before%20the%20country%20got%20independence.%20After%20he%20took%20over%20as%20its%20editor%2C%20Faiz%20found%20himself%20behind%20bars%20for%20allegedly%20plotting%20a%20coup.%20The%20case%20came%20to%20be%20known%20as%20the%20Rawalpindi%20Conspiracy%20Case%2C%20and%20it%20meant%20that%20the%20revered%20poet%20ended%20up%20spending%20four%20years%20in%20different%20jails%20in%20the%20country%20and%20living%20under%20the%20threat%20of%20being%20executed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20poems%20he%20wrote%20from%20prison%2C%20%E2%80%98A%20Prison%20Evening%E2%80%99%2C%20reflects%20the%20spirit%20that%20kept%20him%20going%20through%20that%20experience%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20thought%20keeps%20consoling%20me%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ethough%20tyrants%20may%20command%20that%20lamps%20be%20smashed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20rooms%20where%20lovers%20are%20destined%20to%20meet%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ethey%20cannot%20snuff%20out%20the%20moon%2C%20so%20today%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Enor%20tomorrow%2C%20no%20tyranny%20will%20succeed%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESyed%20Muhammad%20Askari%20%E2%80%93%20with%20whom%20we%20began%20this%20short%20note%20%E2%80%93%20fortunately%20was%20allowed%20to%20return%20after%20over%20a%20day.%20He%20was%20courageous%20enough%20to%20go%20public%20with%20his%20experiences.%20Speaking%20to%20a%20television%20channel%2C%20he%20explained%20how%20he%20was%20first%20blindfolded%2C%20had%20his%20head%20covered%20and%20transferred%20to%20another%20vehicle%20that%20seemed%20to%20go%20around%20in%20circles.%20Finally%20he%20found%20himself%20incarcerated%20in%20a%20small%20room.%20Who%20his%20abductors%20were%20are%20not%20known%2C%20neither%20was%20the%20reason%20for%20why%20he%20was%20abducted%20or%20indeed%20why%20he%20was%20released.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWas%20it%20a%20case%20of%20mistaken%20identity%20or%20just%20a%20plain%2C%20old-fashioned%20way%20to%20intimidate%20the%20independent%20journalist%20in%20him%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWant%20to%20play%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20a%20reputation%20for%20being%20on%20the%20more%20serious%20side%20of%20the%20aisle%20so%20I%20like%20it%20when%20it%20lets%20its%20more%20playful%20aspect%20make%20it%20to%20its%20columns.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDelighted%2C%20therefore%2C%20to%20note%20the%20new%20entrant%2C%20%E2%80%98Questionable%E2%80%99%20(%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fquiz%2Fquestionable-july-16-2023-edition%5C%22%3EQuestionable%E2%80%99%3A%20A%20Quiz%20by%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20July%206%2C%202023%20Edition).%20Of%20course%2C%20being%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20quiz%20is%20not%20entirely%20random%20fun%20stuff%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20about%20news%20and%2C%20yes%20(the%20serious%20part)%20it%20seeks%20to%20fight%20misinformation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20tried%20the%20quiz%20(strictly%20because%20it%20was%20multi-choice%20and%20not%20too%20taxing%20on%20the%20grey%20cells)%20and%20am%20pleased%20to%20declare%20that%20I%20fared%20fairly%20well%20(without%20cheating%20too%20much).%20As%20I%20went%20through%20the%20questionnaire%2C%20I%20realised%20the%20wisdom%20of%20Umberto%20Eco%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.azquotes.com%2Fquote%2F1348391%3Fref%3Dquiz%5C%22%3Eobservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Egeneration%20knew%20pretty%20well%20what%20happened%2050%20years%20before%20its%20birth.%20But%20that%E2%80%99s%20all%20changed%20now.%20He%20said%20he%20followed%20quiz%20programmes%20because%20they%20were%20a%20paramount%20example%20of%20the%20span%20of%20memory%20of%20the%20young%20generation%3A%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20able%20to%20remember%20everything%20that%20happened%20in%20their%20life%20but%20not%20before.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20vouch%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20GenX%20being%20familiar%20with%20everything%20that%20happened%20in%20their%20lifetime.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20seriously%20doubt%20whether%20they%20are%20acquainted%20with%20anything%20that%20has%20not%20already%20appeared%20on%20Insta!%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EReaders%20write%20in%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20is%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%20promoting%20Narendra%20Modi%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELeo%20Levy%20from%20Brussels%20has%20a%20suggestion%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20make%20it%20a%20point%20to%20skip%20all%20media%20images%20that%20showcase%20dictators.%20So%20my%20question%20is%20why%20should%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20not%20make%20an%20active%20effort%20to%20avoid%20all%20photographs%20that%20show%20Narendra%20Modi%3F%20When%20I%20go%20to%20your%20website%20I%20cannot%20but%20notice%20the%20plethora%20of%20images%20of%20the%20present%20prime%20minister%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20the%20theme%20of%20the%20story%20is%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20occasion.%20By%20constantly%20playing%20up%20the%20Modi%20image%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20participating%20willy%20nilly%20in%20extending%20the%20everlasting%20electoral%20campaign%20that%20the%20BJP%20runs.%20Making%20a%20polytheist%20party%E2%80%99s%20god%20invisible%20might%20be%20a%20symbolic%20gesture%20of%20resistance!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDoubt%20if%20the%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20even%20existed%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPriya%C2%A0Chacko%20wants%20to%20know%20the%20source%20of%20a%20claim%20made%20in%20the%20columns%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20coverage%20of%20the%20Khalistan%20movement%20repeats%20other%C2%A0Indian%20media%20outlets%E2%80%99%20claim%20that%C2%A0Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20was%20the%20chief%20of%20the%C2%A0Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20(%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar-killing-khalistan-speculation%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAs%2520for%2520Nijjar%2527s%2520killings%252C%2520the%2Clocal%2520political%2520dispute%2520in%2520Surrey%25E2%2580%259D.%5C%22%3EHardeep%20Nijjar%20is%20Third%20Pro-Khalistani%20Activist%20to%20Die%20Abroad%20in%2045%20Days%2C%20Canada%20Probing%20Motive%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20June%2021).%20What%20is%20the%20source%20of%20this%20information%20apart%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%3F%C2%A0I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20this%20is%20something%20Nijjar%20ever%20claimed%20and%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20little%20public%20evidence%20that%20this%20group%20even%20exists.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDo%20the%20laws%20of%20chemistry%20apply%20to%20media%20toxicity%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDunu%20Roy%C2%A0is%20a%20Chemical%20Engineer%20by%20training%2C%20a%20social%20scientist%20by%20compulsion%20and%20political%20ecologist%20by%20choice.%20This%20is%20his%20take%20on%20hate%20news%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-amit-malviya-new-media-hatred%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Backstory%3A%C2%A0The%20Virality%20of%20Hate%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20New%20Media%20Landscape%20and%20The%20Forces%20Behind%20it%E2%80%99%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20July%201)%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAccording%20to%20the%20principle%20of%20(occupational)%20safety%2C%20there%20are%20two%20ways%20to%20address%20toxicity%3A%20either%20one%20administers%20an%20anti-toxicant%20to%20counter%20the%20symptoms%20of%20toxicity%3B%20or%20one%20tracks%20the%20roots%20of%20the%20toxic%20substance%20and%20eliminates%20it.%20I%20wonder%20how%20this%20principle%20would%20apply%20to%20the%20media%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMy%20response%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20perhaps%20a%20more%20rooted%20approach%20would%20be%20appropriate%E2%80%A6Dunu%20Roy%2C%20who%20set%20up%20the%20Delhi-based%20Hazards%20Centre%2C%20certainly%20brings%20a%20new%20dimension%20to%20perceiving%20toxic%20news%20and%20we%20thank%20him!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20will%20be%20taking%20a%20break%20for%20a%20few%20weeks.%20The%20column%20will%20be%20back%20by%20September%20end.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWrite%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eombudsperson%40thewire.in%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689416152000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15152028%2FUntitled-design-20-1-e1689414652592.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-revisiting-the-ruins-of-kashmirs-media-ahead-of-the-fourth-anniversary-of-august-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20fortnightly%20column%20from%20The%20Wire's%20ombudsperson.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-revisiting-the-ruins-of-kashmirs-media-ahead-of-the-fourth-anniversary-of-august-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22S%20Korea%20floods%20leave%20at%2