ber%20of%20gun%20licences%20issued%20in%20the%20period%20between%202016%20and%202023%20are%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-gun-licenses-biren-singh-violence%3Futm%3Dauthorlistpage%5C%22%3EManipur%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Nagaland.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20the%20states%20which%20had%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20gun%20licence%20holders%20were%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Bihar%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F14449979%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fvisualisation%2F14449979%2F%3Futm_source%3Dembed%26utm_campaign%3Dvisualisation%2F14449979%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Made%20with%20Flourish%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fresources%2Fmade_with_flourish.svg%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20case%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20a%20ban%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20gun%20licences%20was%20imposed%20on%202018.%20This%20was%20lifted%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ban%20was%20put%20in%20place%20following%20a%20gun%20license%20racket%20that%20came%20to%20light%20during%20investigations%20conducted%20by%20the%20Rajasthan%20Police%E2%80%99s%20Anti-Terror%20Squad%20(ATS).%20The%20investigation%20revealed%20the%20involvement%20of%20public%20officials%2C%20particularly%20some%20IAS%20officers.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%2C%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20which%20the%20Union%20government%20made%20into%20a%20Union%20Territory%20in%20August%202019%2C%20is%20leading%20the%20country%20in%20the%20number%20of%20gun%20licences%20issued%20in%20the%20period%20between%202016%20and%202023%20%E2%80%93%201%2C30%2C914.%20Notably%2C%20with%20the%20ban%20in%20place%2C%20licences%20were%20only%20issued%20between%202016%20to%202018%20and%20then%2C%20from%20January%202023%20till%20June%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20total%20number%20of%20gun%20licence%20holders%20in%20the%20UT%20now%20stands%20at%205%2C00%2C105%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20last%20available%20data%20from%20December%202016%2C%20which%20indicated%203%2C69%2C191%20licence%20holders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20October%202020%2C%20the%20Deccan%20Herald%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2Fnorth-and-central%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-continues-to-top-list-in-issuance-of-gun-licences-897466.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Equoted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20official%20data%20and%20stated%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E22%2C805%20fresh%20arms%20licences%20had%20been%20issued%20across%20the%20country%20between%202018%20and%20September%2015%2C%202020%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E17%2C905%20were%20issued%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20which%20accounted%20for%2078.51%25%20of%20the%20licences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20figure%20was%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20asked%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20at%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20as%20to%20how%20it%20could%20explain%20the%20significant%20rise%20in%20the%20issue%20of%20gun%20licences%20in%20the%20UT%2C%20despite%20an%20almost%20five-year%20ban%20in%20place.%20This%20article%20will%20be%20update%20if%20we%20receive%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20RTI%20request%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EMinistry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20The%20Wire%20had%20asked%20for%20y%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eear-wise%20data%20on%20the%20number%20of%20individuals%20holding%20licensed%20guns%20in%20each%20state%20of%20the%20country.%20It%20had%20also%20asked%20for%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0categorisation%20of%20gun%20licences%2C%20such%20as%20licences%20for%20self-defence%2C%20professional%20requirements%2C%20sports%20shooting%2C%20etc.%2C%20and%20the%20number%20of%20licences%20issued%20in%20each%20category%2C%20state-wise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20response%20received%20only%20had%20data%20on%20gun%20licences%20issued%20in%20each%20state.%20It%20showed%20that%20as%20of%20June%2020%20this%20year%2C%20there%20were%2037.7%20lakh%20active%20gun%20licences%20across%20the%20country.%20This%20is%20over%204%20lakhs%20more%20than%20the%20licences%20that%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-has-33-69-lakh-gun-licences-uttar-pradesh-tops-list-with-12-77-lakh%2Fstory-uRQ9XGCy9wpczOiEMcFmAN.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eactive%20in%20December%202016%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20when%20data%20was%20last%20made%20publicly%20available.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENotably%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20the%20only%20Union%20Territory%20with%20a%20high%20number%20of%20gun%20license%20holders%20in%20the%20country%2C%20while%20Lakshadweep%20has%20zero%20licence%20holders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20following%20are%20the%20figures%20for%20gun%20licenses%20in%20other%20Union%20Territories%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EUT%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EGun%20licence%20holders%20in%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%3Cspan%3EChandigarh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%3Cspan%3E6%2C794%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%3Cspan%3EDelhi%20(not%20a%20UT%20but%20a%20NCT)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C