ng-soldiers-in-belarus%2Farticleshow%2F101762736.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussias-wagner-fighters-are-training-soldiers-in-belarus%2Famp_articleshow%2F101762736.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussias-wagner-fighters-are-training-soldiers-in-belarus%2Famp_articleshow%2F101762736.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20How%20Does%20India%E2%80%99s%20First%20AI-Based%20Driverless%20Car%20Work%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EImagine%20a%20driverless%20car%20carrying%20passengers%20cruising%20on%20roads.%20It%20sounds%20like%20something%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304074%2Fbook-recommendations-by-ira-mukhoty-on-history-science-wolf-hall%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrom%20a%20sci-fi%20novel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20company%20Minus%20Zero%20has%20made%20it%20possible!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20co-founders%2C%20Gagandeep%20Reehal%20and%20Gursimran%20Kalra%2C%20were%20in%20college%20when%20the%20idea%20of%20building%20something%20as%20futuristic%20as%20a%20driverless%20car%20came%20to%20them.%20With%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20the%20duo%20started%20Minus%20Zero%20%E2%80%94%20an%20AI%20mobility%20company%20and%20built%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20self-driving%20car%20called%20%E2%80%98zPod%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWondering%20how%20the%20car%20works%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20a%20network%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F124905%2Fartificial-intelligence-cctv-cameras-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-resolution%20cameras%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20are%20strategically%20placed%20on%20the%20car.%20These%20cameras%20capture%20real-time%20images%20of%20their%20surroundings%20and%20t