s.%20This%20same%20concept%20is%20used%20for%20the%20upholstery%20of%20the%20furniture%20at%20Daera.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDaera-X-Cancelled-Plans-1689080816.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22L%20to%20R%3A%20Sharon%2C%20Mallika%20and%20Jannat%2C%20the%20trio%20behind%20the%20collaborative%20collection%20Daera%20X%20Cancelled%20Plans%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDaera-X-Cancelled-Plans-1689080816.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDaera-X-Cancelled-Plans-1689080816-169x300.jpg%20169w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDaera-X-Cancelled-Plans-1689080816-500x889.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDaera-X-Cancelled-Plans-1689080816-768x1365.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDaera-X-Cancelled-Plans-1689080816-864x1536.jpg%20864w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDaera-X-Cancelled-Plans-1689080816-150x267.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323405%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EL%20to%20R%3A%20Sharon%2C%20Mallika%20and%20Jannat%2C%20the%20trio%20behind%20the%20collaborative%20collection%20Daera%20X%20Cancelled%20Plans%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Sharon%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20waste%20is%20sourced%20from%20industrial%20areas%20in%20and%20around%20Delhi%20and%20Hyderabad.%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20lived%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20I%20am%20familiar%20with%20the%20manufacturing%20industries%20here.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20started%20sourcing%20waste%20from%20the%20same%20pharmaceuti