enhouse-gas-help-farmers-string-bio-startup-ezhil-subbian%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaundry%20business%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20I%20looked%20for%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20laundry%20problem%20in%20the%20hotel%2C%20I%20started%20researching%20the%20market.%20I%20found%20that%20the%20industry%20was%20unorganised%2C%20and%20there%20were%20no%20professional%20players%20other%20than%20our%20neighbourhood%20%3Cem%3Edhobis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20RedSeer%E2%80%99s%20research%20report%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Laundry%20Services%20Market%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20laundry%20market%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%20to%20%2415%20billion%20by%202025%E2%80%9D.%20Out%20of%20this%2C%20the%20organised%20sector%20is%20less%20than%20five%20percent%20of%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20take%20up%20the%20opportunity%20to%20organise%20the%20laundry%20industry%20and%20offer%20%E2%80%98quality%20and%20consistent%20services%E2%80%99.%20Arunabh%20quit%20his%20job%20in%20August%202016%2C%20and%20they%20launched%20a%20laundromat%20service%20called%20UClean%20in%20January%202017%20with%20a%20capital%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%2C%20which%20has%20grown%20to%20a%20Rs%20100%20crore%20business%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20microentrepreneurs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-10T195520.867-1688999319.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20uclean%20store%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-10T195520.867-1688999319.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-10T195520.867-1688999319-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-10T195520.867-1688999319-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-10T195520.867-1688999319-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-10T195520.867-1688999319-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323280%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EUClean%20has%20350%2B%20stores%20across%20100%20cities.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20seed%20sown%20in%20their%20minds%20of%20doing%20something%20in%20the%20laundry%20industry%2C%20Faridabad-based%20Gunjan%20and%20Arunabh%20took%20inspiration%20from%20the%20flourishing%20laundromat%20culture%20in%20South%20East%20Asian%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20travelled%20to%20Indonesia%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20Thailand%20and%20Singapore%2C%20and%20found%20the%20laundry%20industry%20thriving.%20Indonesia%20was%20really%20an%20eye-opener.%20In%20India%2C%20most%20give%20their%20clothes%20outside%20for%20ironing.%20So%20we%20wondered%2C%20%E2%80%98Then%20why%20not%20for%20washing%3F%E2%80%99%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20we%20realised%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20more%20of%20a%20supply%20problem%20than%20demand%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Gunjan%2C%20co-founder%20and%20head%20of%20product%20and%20marketing%2C%20UClean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20attempts%20to%20uberise%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321740%2Fmother-daughters-dea-ojasvi-hema-sharma-chilzo-mumbai-global-cuisines-sauces-condiments%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaundry%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20early%202010s%2C%20but%20logistics%20remained%20a%20major%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20these%20laundry%20businesse